Well I agree. This is not for the younger Cape Verdeans. It falls short of explaining why foreign countries hate Cape Verde and have for 250 years. I am no activist and Cape Verde's corruption bores me. It gives politicians all the reason in the world to keep the status quo in our news as stated by others and to show us how civilized they really are! In the grand scope of things, Cape Verde is like a poor second rate country. So what? We are ignored by powerful nations most of the time. Why should we do more than they do and not expect the same?
